title: Imac 27 2010 no USB
message: Enable is supposed to be low. Did you check 5V on USB connectors?

title: Imac 27 2010 no USB
message: pin 1 on J4630? nothing on any of the pins

title: Imac 27 2010 no USB
message: Well, if U4600/01 pin 3 and 4 are low and 5V is coming in on pin 2 there should be output on pin 6. So looks like dead U4600/01, but I have never seen them both fail.
